extends layout

block content
  a(href='/') ‚Üê Back to recipes
  //- 1. Dynamically display a recipe name
  h1= `${recipe.recipe_name}`

  //- 2. Render the `src` attribute using the `image_url` property
  img(src=`${recipe.image_url}` width='320' height='240')

  //- 3. Dynamically display a recipe description
  p= `${recipe.description}`

  h2 Ingredients
  ul
    //- 4. Use Pug's `each` iterator to render an `<li>` for each ingredient
    each ingredient in recipe.ingredients 
      li= ingredient

  h2 Steps
  ol
    //- 5. Use an iterator to render an `<li>` for each recipe step
    each step in recipe.steps 
      li= step

